Patch Set 2:

With:

https://review.openstack.org/#/c/34801/33/glance/store/swift.py,

we get the 'scrubbed credentials' which is still not something we really wish to expose to the user.

For example if the set location functionality is enabled then a user who knows the scrubbed credentials can potentially download somebody else's image by setting the location as swift+https://scrubbed:creds:/<any image id>.
